{"tid":2300307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲鋼琴教師非禮五歲女童被判緩刑","createTime":"2020-11-25T11:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T13:10:38.000Z","uid":72280,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17223f8b2e8fa6798977406a84cf3c05fef9f9bd","tid":2300307,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"一名23歲的前鋼琴教師因為非禮年僅五歲的女學生而被控。法官考慮到他患有阿斯伯格綜合徵，判處他緩刑三年。<br />\n這起案件發生在2016年，被告當時是受害人的鋼琴老師，每星期以一對一的方式給女孩上課。他在同年8月份時，以調整女孩的坐姿為藉口，趁機把手伸進女孩的內褲觸摸她的私處。<br />\n女孩回家後向母親申訴在排尿的時候感覺疼痛，並最終告訴母親事發的經過，才揭發被告的罪行。<br />\n被告在緩刑期間晚上11點之後不得外出，而且必須履行一千個小時的社區服務。他也必須遠離為兒童而設的教育機構或中心，刪除社交媒體帳號內的所有猥褻色情內容，並在家中的互聯網設備中裝置過濾軟件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/probation-for-former-piano-teacher-aspergers-syndrome-who-molested-5-year-old-student-1317666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8world.com%2Fnews%2Fsingapore%2Farticle%2Fprobation-for-former-piano-teacher-aspergers-syndrome-who-molested-5-year-old-student-1317666&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwsE4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=10fb9549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/probation-for-former-piano-teacher-aspergers-syndrome-who-molested-5-year-old-student-1317666</a>"},{"pid":"4b3f79ef5d60606d97fdd502f1ffa3e8d43a030b","tid":2300307,"uid":199670,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:55:24.000Z","msg":"cls邊個連登仔<br />\n5歲都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d657cf4f5bc2b3fefa0d61e30ce3dba4c913e5c","tid":2300307,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b832395523b388c9d7d00c482f3066797e5c99b